BufferLimit 128m

IMAPAccount kdecherf
Host imap.fastmail.com
User kevin@kdecherf.com
PassCmd "gpg --decrypt /home/kdecherf/.mail/.fm.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore kdecherf-remote
Account kdecherf

MaildirStore kdecherf-local
Path ~/.mail/kdecherf/
Inbox ~/.mail/kdecherf/INBOX
Flatten .
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel kdecherf
Master :kdecherf-remote:
Slave :kdecherf-local:
Patterns * "!*Archive/%"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes

Channel kdecherf-archive
Master :kdecherf-remote:
Slave :kdecherf-local:
Patterns "*Archive/%"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
CopyArrivalDate yes
